{"id": 2465, "genre": 1004, "title": "【好奇心X新福特翼虎】测测你有潜质成为哪一款老司机？", "description": "可能会透露出你内心的秘密，不信来测！（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 12410, "comment_count": 42, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180716104241lpaXDUgGbyd7CFIR.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-07-16T04:18:00Z", "column": null, "normal_questions": [{"id": 4511, "content": "以下哪种情况下最让你感到生气？", "image": "img/question/question/20180716101114lRSYfDmF2Qr0zjbI.gif", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 292788, "title": "路见不平一声吼啊", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 292789, "title": "当发现最亲密的人对自己有了欺骗", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 292790, "title": "开车在路上发现强行变道的", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 292791, "title": "工作中背了黑锅", "score": 0.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 4512, "content": "以下哪种情况会让你觉得最有安全感？", "image": "img/question/question/201807161023000AgGosrbVzXTNYd9.gif", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 292792, "title": "有人安排好所有事，你都不用考虑", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 292793, "title": "自己的事情自己全部规划好，掌控住", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 292794, "title": "呆在熟悉的环境中，没有陌生人都是认识的人", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 292795, "title": "旅行一段时间，终于回到了家里", "score": 0.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 4513, "content": "你通常会因为什么样的理由去开始一场旅行？", "image": "img/question/question/20180716102521ncOByZjM7RWXFTUu.gif", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 292796, "title": "工作让自己找不到人生的方向了", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 292797, "title": "纯粹就是因为有空 ", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 292798, "title": "每年一定要有的放松啊", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 292799, "title": "正好有了可以一起出行的玩伴", "score": 0.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 4514, "content": "当开车遇上大堵车，你会？", "image": "img/question/question/20180716102807N8BQWMV6ktZndx2z.GIF", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 292800, "title": "顺其自然，就堵着吧", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 292801, "title": "一定要给自己找点事情干", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 292802, "title": "不接受堵车这件事，不会在可能堵车的时候出门", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 292803, "title": "很生气，一路生气回去", "score": 0.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 4515, "content": "以下几种开车行为，你最接近哪种？", "image": "img/question/question/20180716102942PdwqoKCiUg0BJ1el.gif", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 292804, "title": "仔仔细细，不踩线不越界", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 292806, "title": "狂野开，马路都是我的舞台", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 292807, "title": "经常容易被惹的很不开心", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 292808, "title": "随意吧，挺佛系的", "score": 0.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 4516, "content": "什么样的车，让你开起来最轻松？", "image": "img/question/question/201807161033354QlJqf7Z8pUwERxD.gif", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 292809, "title": "安全性能好的车", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 292813, "title": "动力，操控性能好的车", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 292814, "title": "宽敞明亮的车", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 292815, "title": "小车", "score": 0.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 4518, "content": "什么情况下，你会选择开车出行？", "image": "img/question/question/20180716105231xCtPalSphJ6LIFRz.gif", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 292816, "title": "天气不方便出行的时候", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 292817, "title": "天气不错，想开车顺便兜兜风的时候", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 292818, "title": "看路程决定", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 292819, "title": "不堵车的时候", "score": 0.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 4519, "content": "你最不能允许什么样行为出现在车内？", "image": "img/question/question/20180716105330kTNSahxywDdr7iL4.gif", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 292820, "title": "吃东西！", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 292821, "title": "你在开车对方在睡觉", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 292822, "title": "在车内听一些难听的音乐", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 292823, "title": "在车内脱鞋子", "score": 0.0, "image": null}]}]}